<p><strong>Context:</strong> This decoupling is the most important finding in our study. AI Overviews do not simply repackage the top organic results. They use a separate extraction and ranking system that values different signals.</p>
<p>What this means for your strategy: you need to optimize for AI citation independently of organic ranking. The tactics overlap, but they are not identical. A page that ranks #1 but lacks schema markup, named sources, and structured answer blocks may never appear in AI Overviews. A page that ranks #15 but has all three signals can still earn citations.</p>
